      "description_short": "A complete cross-platform rideshare solution combining driver, customer, and admin systems with payments, navigation, chat and real-time dispatch logic.",
      "description_long": "Geo Go is a full end-to-end rideshare ecosystem built to support customers, drivers, and operational staff through a single unified platform. The project includes a combined driver and passenger app, an administrative web panel, a secure backend dispatch engine, automated payment flows, and real-time communication features.\n\nDrivers receive live trip requests, in-app turn-by-turn navigation powered by Mapbox, trip history tracking, manual payout tools, chat, and customer rating flows. Customers can request rides, track drivers in real time, view full trip details, apply vouchers, and manage future bookings. The administrative web panel includes user management, vehicle & pricing controls, payment history, voucher management, and operational oversight tools.\n\nA custom backend handles dispatch logic, trip assignment, location updates, payment processing, and system-wide security protections.",
